# Templates CGL

Questa cartella contiene i template ufficiali del CGL (Cognitive Governance Layer).  
Ogni template è disponibile in due versioni:

- **Standard** — include la struttura completa del framework.
- **Compilabile** — versione ridotta con campi da riempire.

## Struttura
templates/ it/ cgl-prompt-template.md cgl-prompt-template-fillable.md en/ cgl-prompt-template.md cgl-prompt-template-fillable.m


## Uso

1. Scegli la lingua.
2. Scegli il formato (standard o compilabile).
3. Copia il template nel tuo prompt.
4. Compila le sezioni richieste.


English

# CGL Templates

This folder contains the official templates for the CGL (Cognitive Governance Layer).  
Each template is available in two formats:

- **Standard** — full structure of the framework.  
- **Fillable** — reduced version with fields to complete.

## Structure
templates/ it/ cgl-prompt-template.md cgl-prompt-template-fillable.md en/ cgl-prompt-template.md cgl-prompt-template-fillable.md

## How to use

1. Choose the language.  
2. Choose the format (standard or fillable).  
3. Copy the template into your prompt.  
4. Fill in the required sections.





